headline: TE Connectivity declares quarterly dividend
summary: TE Connectivity plc (NYSE: TEL) announced today that its board of directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.71 per ordinary share, payable on March 13, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 20, 2026.
